ygData.messageBody:
>Easy to test, play DDD underneath the 'birdhouse' in S Karana and see what
>comes runnin' }:>


Haha. I did this directly under the birdhouse right after I got DDD,
forgetting about the XYZ axis thingie. I died too quick to make out what it
was that killed me, since so many birds were whacking me, but the guildmate
I was grouped with remarked on how the vendor at the top of the birdhouse
came all the way down just to smack me.

You'd have thought I told him his mother wore army boots or something ;-P


-Treehugger and Songmaker
